name: see-through one-piece swimsuit
description:
Disclaimers: The moderators kindly ask me to remove sex related pictures of anime "young" girls in showcase, well, what can I say, these are standard anime girl faces, you put only "1girl" in positive prompts, you will get a "young" anime girl with any anime checkpoint model by default, cause that's how anime girls ought to be drawed, even they might be 500 years old. So I have to put a mask on them, then they can´t be judged by faces. I don't really want to add any figure prompt. Anyways, you can view my profile page and find out my pixiv site.

The original model is temporarily removed by moderator, I reupload a 6 epochs version

I start a poll the model training in the future. This poll is open to everyone, so you can remain anonymous. https://www.patreon.com/posts/what-kind-of-do-83968613

I checked prompts see-through, school swimsuit by default, the results are usually breasts out, or weird swimsuit with two tones,like

(deleted as moderators ask)

Still, it not prefect,but better. Compared to the default, this LoRA increases the probability that the swimsuit will stay the same tone
